interactions with these extraterrestrials?&nbsp;
I asked him. And how did you communicate&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:03.440 --> 00:23:10.240
with them? In what language? He said, "At some&nbsp;
subconscious level." Interesting. And did you&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:10.240 --> 00:23:16.880
learn anything else about the exact communication&nbsp;
between him and the extraterrestrials? Did he ask&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:16.880 --> 00:23:22.240
them any questions and learn any interesting&nbsp;
information that he then relayed to you? A&nbsp;&nbsp;

