difficult question. Well, you see, communication&nbsp;
probably happens through thoughts, most likely,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:29.520 --> 00:23:37.600
but he didn't tell me much. Maybe there were some&nbsp;
secrets. Secrets from everyone else. Because he&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:37.600 --> 00:23:45.520
communicated with them privately, you could say.&nbsp;
So why was my state normal? Not surprised. Well,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:45.520 --> 00:23:50.480
because I was there, probably on purpose. They&nbsp;
probably have this effect so that a person&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:50.480 --> 00:23:58.480
doesn't go crazy. So they don't take them to a&nbsp;
