FID, which now includes about 200 countries. I was&nbsp;
also a senator and a member of the Parliament of&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:25:07.520 --> 00:25:16.000
the Russian Federation. I visited other countries&nbsp;
both officially and unofficially and I had many&nbsp;&nbsp;

