with the former president of the Soviet Union,&nbsp;
Mikail Gorbachov, he also spoke about the fact&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:25:46.480 --> 00:25:54.800
that there are various civilizations that have&nbsp;
made contact with representatives of our earth.

