right away that I met them. I thought for a long&nbsp;
time about whether to say it or not. After all,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:28.240
at that time in 1997, I held many official&nbsp;
positions. I was also the president of the Russian&nbsp;&nbsp;

